Class ArraySpectrum

  • java.lang.Object
    • Spectrum.Spectrum
      • Spectrum.ArraySpectrum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Spectrum>

    public class ArraySpectrum
extends Spectrum
    Array implementation of a spectrum can be used for fast processing of spectrum instead of looping through a list of peak object in traditional spectrum (Note: only computing cosine is supported, add in other as needed)
